extends layout

block content
  div(class="row")
    div(class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1")
      form
        div(class="form-group")
          label(for="to-do")
            | I have something to do now... :
          textarea(rows="5",class="form-control",id="to-do",placeholder="Just tell us what you want to do and we will help.")
        div(class="text-center")
          a(type="submit",class="btn btn-primary")
            | Help me with this!
          a(type="submit",class="btn btn-info")
            | Save for later
    div(class="col-md-5")
      form
        div(class="form-group")
          label
            | Stuff I have to do.
            a(href="#",target="_modal")
              | See all tasks
        table(class="table table-condensed table-hover")
          thead
            tr
              th
                | Task
              th
                | Time?
              th
                | Location?
          tbody
            tr
              td
                | Go to the Arena cinema with John tomorrow at 8:00
              td
                | April 19th 8:00AM
              td
                | Cinema Arena 
                a(target="_modal",href="#")
                  | (map)
            tr(class="danger")
              td
                span(class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign",aria-hidden="true")
                | Call Jenny this afternoon
              td
                | April 18th 4:00PM
              td
            tr
              td
                | Buy vodka for this evening
              td
                | April 18th 8:00PM
              td
                a(target="_modal",href="#")
                  | Recommend
  div(class="row")
    div(class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center")
      hr
  div(class="row")
    div(class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-1")
      h3
        | You can meetup with 
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          | John
      p
        | Both you and 
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          | John
        | will be together at 
        a(href="#" target="_modal")
          | Borisova Gradina
        | at 5:00 Monday
      iframe(width="100%",height="250",frameborder="0",style="border:0",src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?q=Sofia&key=AIzaSyBHGpzUbuMA_LU4jrOikW_EEhIyXpVA2ZU")
    div(class="col-md-4")
      h3
        | Bad weather warning for 20th April
      p 
        | A bad weather
        span(style="color:#aaaaff")
          | 12 C with
        span(style="color:light-blue")
          | rain
        | is expected for 20th April, should you reconsider going to 
        a(href="#" target="_modal")
          | Zapaden Park
      img(class="weather-forecast-img",src="/content/rain.png")
    div(class="col-md-3")
      h3
        | Place to buy
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          |  vodka
        | nearby
      p
        | There are 
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          | places nearby
        | which sell
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          |  vodka
        | you can do the 
        a(href="#",target="_modal")
          | Pick up a vodka on my wa...
        | task.
      iframe(width="100%",height="250",frameborder="0",style="border:0",src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?q=Sofia%20NDK&key=AIzaSyBHGpzUbuMA_LU4jrOikW_EEhIyXpVA2ZU")
  div(class="row")
    div(class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center")
      br
      | Was this autohelp usefull? You can see all 
      a(href="#",target="_modal")
        | autohelp
      | for your 
      a(href="#" target="_modal")
        | upcomming tasks


